songs.title: Overjoyed (Ghostwriter Remix)
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Have, have
Whooa, who-oa who-oa
Whooa, who-oa who-oa

[Verse 1]
W-w-words are all we
(Whooa, who-oa who-oa)
W-w-words are all we have
(Whooa, who-oa who-oa)
W-w-words are all we
(Whooa, who-oa who-oa)
W-w-words are all we have
(Whooa, who-oa who-oa)

[Chorus]
Oh I hear you calling in the dead of night
(Have, have)
Oh I hear you calling in the dead of night
Oh I feel overjoyed
(H-h-have)

[Verse 2]
Oh I feel overjoyed
(Joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed)
(Joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed)

[Verse 3]
(Whooa, who-oa who-oa)
Oh I feel overjoyed
(Have, have, h-h-have)
(Have, have, h-h-have)

[Outro]
Oh I feel overjoyed
(Joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed)
Oh I hear you calling in the dead of night
(Joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed)
Oh I hear you calling in the dead of night
(Have, have)
Oh I feel overjoyed
(Joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed)
(Joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed, joyed)
